Package com.skobbler.ngx.poitracker

Contains classes for tracking pois during navigation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SKPOITrackerListener
    Listener for POI Tracker callbacks.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SKDetectedPOI
    Class that stores information about a detected POI by the SKPOITracker.
    SKPOITrackerManager
    Class that manages the POIs tracking
    SKTrackablePOI
    SKTrackablePOI provides the model object of a trackable POI, used by the SKPOITracker.
    SKTrackablePOIRule
    The rule on detecting POIs.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SKTrackablePOIType
    POITracker POI types
